name: NAJ in HSP2
description: A translation into HSP2 by Hans Verhaegen of “Not Another Jpeg”, a text written by M Plummer-Fernández on 9-4-21 ( https://www.plummerfernandez.com/works/not-another-jpeg/) in which ‘he touches the ontological & practical shifts NFTs represent for artists, as well as the role Tezos/ @hicetnunc can play in alleviating the ecological toll of PoW blockchains’ (wording by @JesseDamiani). www.hansup.be
